{"tid":779195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港四大猛鬼屋邨】網民：呢條邨猛到日頭都撞嘢","createTime":"2018-08-14T08:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T13:18:10.000Z","uid":160807,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"68ea8fb171042c12570b4745e52663df34a6f859","tid":779195,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:50:58.000Z","msg":"撰文：環球膠報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/21_9038014225b3e15e23b018.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F21_9038014225b3e15e23b018.jpg&h=e7fca964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港樓價貴到hihi，土地問題又嚴重，公屋最少都要排5年以上，所以好多人都唔驚住凶宅，寧願入住靈異公屋。不過咁又真啊，真係要驚都係驚要訓街多啲啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港四大最靈異屋苑</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/1_meitu_1_3507438035b3e5d455625d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F1_meitu_1_3507438035b3e5d455625d.jpg&h=23b79a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講起凶宅就一定會諗起鬼故，以前夜晚聽電台講鬼故好過癮架，不過依家好少人聽電台架喇。不過靈異故仔真係長青題材，講極都講唔完。最近有人係facebook group講起「香港邊個屋苑最邪」，引起一班靈異迷講出自己個屋苑嘅故仔。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>柴灣 &ndash; 漁灣邨<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/ed1_16571011785b3e12f377879.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fed1_16571011785b3e12f377879.png&h=c3068cea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;試過家姐出咗去無返屋企一段時間，有晚我聽到家姐把聲喺門口嗌我個名，叫我開門，我同老豆講，老豆話無，點都唔肯開門。但我一直聽到家姐叫我開門，最後老豆開門畀我睇，乜人都無，嗰陣我突然好驚，驚到衝上床係咁喊，老豆話唔係家姐，仲話過咗5點（凌晨）就無事㗎啦！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;有次我返屋企，點知行出升降機開始就覺得有人跟住我，但成條走廊得我一個行，行到一半覺得後面跟得我好近。我擰轉頭望，都未擰哂就望到牆上好似有個黑影攬埋嚟，當時我個人震晒，開始腳軟。但事實係無人，之後我就極速返屋企。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/3_meitu_3_15519630025b3e5e6aec540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F3_meitu_3_15519630025b3e5e6aec540.jpg&h=3724105e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/6_meitu_6_3551976885b3e5e7e4037f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F6_meitu_6_3551976885b3e5e7e4037f.jpg&h=242bd967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屯門-友愛邨</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/ed_17610036535b3e12f9452d1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2Fed_17610036535b3e12f9452d1.png&h=4d7c8f93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我住喺最盡頭嗰間屋，打橫一排其他單位，好記得有晚係農曆七月十四，當晚6點幾媽咪煮緊飯，屋企打開木門，當年屋邨個個都係開住木門的。我坐係門口隔離梳化睇電視，突然好大聲「嘭」一聲撞向我鐵閘，就好似有個足球踢過來，我即起身望，無人！鐵閘仲郁緊&hellip;.. 就算有人由門口跑去樓梯走都有3個單位距離，無可能我一望係咩人都無&hellip;.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;有一晚，呢個超驚，我瞓瞓下好似醒左，感覺自己好似成個人慢慢升起左，我好大力想瞓返落床但唔得，之後個人瞓住咁轉圈，轉咗一個圈，又慢慢落返去，仲有把男人聲講好唔好玩，之後感覺到自己瞓返落床，就即郁得返，即刻轉身打側唔敢郁，嚇到天光&hellip;&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/8_meitu_8_18577987335b3e5e989ed0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F8_meitu_8_18577987335b3e5e989ed0e.jpg&h=a61b97df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/10_meitu_10_20311841145b3e5ebc3ef36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F10_meitu_10_20311841145b3e5ebc3ef36.jpg&h=57982fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">觀塘 &ndash; 秀茂坪</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/_17231671175b3e12f6808d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F_17231671175b3e12f6808d7.jpg&h=e7d0daab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我聽我媽講過一件很邪的事件，我父母以前經常去某一座飲茶，識到另外兩公婆，每早必定一起飲茶暢談，但有成個月沒有見到他們，心中覺得奇怪，終於有一朝早只見到老婆沒見到老公，我媽就問她的老公如何，為何他不來飲茶，她很傷心的說她老公死了，他們家住38座16樓，她說有一朝早起床看到有一條好大的蛇在廚房裡打蛇餅，他們很驚，於是煲了一煲滾水倒在蛇上想淥死它，蛇是死了，但到晚上她的老公也死了，我媽說那條蛇是找替身，來索命的，有靈邪附在蛇上，聽完當堂毛管凍。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/2_meitu_2_2445850075b3e5e5c6696b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F2_meitu_2_2445850075b3e5e5c6696b.jpg&h=7d71b9e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/9_meitu_9_3545505305b3e5eabea7b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F9_meitu_9_3545505305b3e5eabea7b8.jpg&h=ecfa69a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/12_meitu_12_18435882105b3e5ecea7b32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F12_meitu_12_18435882105b3e5ecea7b32.jpg&h=e2351935&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">荃灣 &ndash; 綠楊新邨</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/_18603664295b3e12f780dc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F_18603664295b3e12f780dc5.jpg&h=b324de0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;嗰時我讀緊小學，我係住16樓，但我放學撘返屋企係一個人，我㩒咗16樓返屋企時候，升降機居然停咗喺9樓。開咗門但無人嘅，我以為關咗門會上返16樓，點知落返地下。我再㩒返16樓返屋企，又係喺9樓開門，又係無人嘅，又自動落返地下。嗰陣仲未知咩事嘅，個看更叫我撘第二部，終於返到屋企。返到去同屋企人講我撞鬼，升降機停咗喺9樓上唔到嚟，屋企人唔信我，之後聽返原來9樓有個婆婆過咗身，之後屋企人先信我撞鬼！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/14_meitu_14_13003138295b3e5ee06f388.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F14_meitu_14_13003138295b3e5ee06f388.jpg&h=02cafd5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.plastichubdaily.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/13_meitu_13_5624410375b3e5ee35fba5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.plastichubdaily.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F13_meitu_13_5624410375b3e5ee35fba5.jpg&h=bc898be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面的屋苑邊個最邪就真係唔知啦，亦都唔想知。不過最尾有巴打突破盲腸話：我怕無樓多過怕住凶宅囉！你話香港人幾咁可悲？"},{"pid":"19fbc75edee674069eec678ff0b4b4edc243da6b","tid":779195,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee2e54d8c3b806fb18dd0b2cd52d1370afa38143","tid":779195,"uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:55:31.000Z","msg":"觀龍樓都無？"},{"pid":"5480fd48aeece84edfc2b408010ebcee1de8fbc3","tid":779195,"uid":7741,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"19fbc75edee674069eec678ff0b4b4edc243da6b","tid":779195,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"算屋邨咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92566c4ada6c24e73a5ca44a09a2815912407f45","tid":779195,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T08:56:33.000Z","msg":"華富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08c4ef0f2b957cba30010381eaa07835161272b","tid":779195,"uid":8783,"li